Chad Stahelski https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chad_Stahelski 0 Chad Stahelski (born September 20, 1968) is an American stuntman and film director. He is known for directing the 2014 film John Wick along with David Leitch, and doubling for Brandon Lee after the fatal accident involving Lee on the set of The Crow (1994). He has also worked as a stunt coordinator and second unit director on several films. Chad_Stahelski ( born September_20_,_1968 ) is an_American_stuntman_and_film_director .
